{
  "stem": "95.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There's a plaque in the front of the house right now that shows how many people were deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It says on the plaque, in memory of the 112 inhabitants of this house, including 40 young children, deported and dead in German camps in 1942. 118 People were deported from this apartment house.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Only six came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And none of the grownups made it-- two young girls and four young boys, who are still living.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I still keep in contact with them, with all of them, these-- these five other people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that night, they took us to the police station, and we sat on benches.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nobody was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Women were just taking care of their cranky children, trying to put them back to sleep, because by now it's 10:30, 11 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And men just-- I don't know what they were thinking, because we were guarded by the French policeman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Nobody can get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They won't let us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They won't let us escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the next morning-- into buses again and sent to Drancy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And what a-- what a horrible revelation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "First of all, Drancy was a compound building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were building apartment building-- apartment houses there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was a huge compound.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were-- it was not finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They had no-- just big holes for windows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was no furniture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was straw on the floor, no doors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there we are with thousands of Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were thousands of Jews waiting to be deported, and straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we arrive there, and it's, again, chaos, tumult, just screaming, crying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "People were asking about their family who were-- who were arrested before them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We asked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My mother asked about my sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
